queries.text:
WITH txt_query AS (
    SELECT 
        c_text, 
        to_tsquery('english', $1) AS query,
        to_tsvector('english', c_text) AS tsv
    FROM postgres_string_types 
    WHERE c_text @@ to_tsquery('english', $1)
)

SELECT txt_query.c_text, txt_query.query, txt_query.tsv, ts_rank(tsv, query) AS rnk
FROM txt_query
ORDER BY rnk DESC
LIMIT 1
queries.name: GetPostgresStringTypesTextSearch

queries.text:
WITH grouped_json_types AS (
    SELECT
        c_uuid,
        c_json::text AS c_json,
        c_jsonb::text AS c_jsonb,
        COUNT(*) AS cnt
    FROM postgres_special_types
    GROUP BY
        c_uuid,
        c_json::text,
        c_jsonb::text
)

SELECT 
    c_uuid, 
    c_json::json AS c_json, 
    c_jsonb::jsonb AS c_jsonb, 
    cnt
FROM grouped_json_types
LIMIT 1
queries.name: GetPostgresSpecialTypesCnt
